{"type":"message","id":"477dbdd9","parentId":"14af649d","timestamp":"2026-05-08T06:56:53.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me understand the current structure vs what the user proposed.\n\nCurrent structure under ~/.openclaw/:\n- openclaw.json (main config)\n- agents/ - agents/ - skills/ - workspace/ (currently has 45 session workspaces)\n- plugins/ - plugin-skills/ - backpkps, canvas, clawpanel, completions, credentials, cron, delivery-queue, devices, extensions, feishu, flows, identity, logs, media, memory, npm, openclaw-weixin, pre-restore, session-delivery-queue, tasks, etc.\n\nWithin workspace/, there are many workspaces including:\n- workspace-main\n- workspace-selector\n- And many date-indexed workspaces like 2026-04-10 through 2026-05-04\n\nThe user's proposed structure:\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── openclaw.json           # 全局路由和通道配置\n├── skills/                 # 全局技能库（放 nano-banana-pro, seedance2.0 等）\n├── workspace-lead/         # 大总管工作区 (含 SOUL.md, AGENTS.md)\n\n\n├── workspace-geo/          # GEO内容优化师工作区\n├── workspace-reddit/       # Reddit营销专家工作区\n└── workspace-tiktok/      # TikTok爆款编导工作区\n```\n\nSo the user's proposal essentially moves to a named workspace model where each specialized agent (lead, geo, reddit, tiktok) has its own dedicated workspace with SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, and other configuration files rather than being mixed into the general session directories.\n\nI should also consider how this overlaps with the current skills structure in workspace/skills/ and the plugin-skills directory at the top level. The user might be consolidating these separate workspace directories while potentially flattening or reorganizing the skills layer. The current workspace/ folder with 45 session workspaces suggests there's some migration or consolidation needed here. I need to clarify what the user is actually proposing here. They're suggesting a simpler directory structure, but I should ask them directly what he envisions and whether he wants to consolidate everything into just those five workspaces or if there are other aspects I'm missing.\n\nLooking at this more carefully, the user seems to want the workspaces themselves to be self-contained with their own SOUL.md and AGENTS.md files, rather than having separate skill directories. I should ask him to clarify the full scope and whether there are additional components he wants to include or if this is the complete picture.\n","thinkingSignature":"b4605a1a671299b8bc5d92878bc36feed1828c79d0ad9a0d0d53d79f303bc11e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你提的结构更清晰——**每个 Agent 有自己独立的工作区**，上下文完全隔离，不串。\n\n当前结构的问题：\n- `workspace/` 下堆了45个会话目录（date-indexed），没有角色语义\n- 大总管和子 Agent 共享同一个 workspace，MEMORY/SOUL 会互相渗透\n- Skills 散在 `workspace/skills` 和 `plugin-skills/`，没有统一归属\n\n---\n\n**你的方案优点：**\n| 维度 | 现状 | 你的方案 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 上下文隔离 | 差（共享workspace） | ✅ 好 |\n| 角色语义 | 弱（date-indexed目录） | ✅ 强 |\n| 扩展性 | 一般 | ✅ 加新Agent只需建目录 |\n| 多人/多团队 | 基本不支持 | ✅ 可对应分配workspace |\n\n**需要注意的点：**\n1. **skills 的归属** —— skills 是共享的还是在各 workspace 里单独放？建议全局 skills 放在 `~/.openclaw/skills/`，各 workspace 只放自己的 SOUL.md/AGENTS.md/MEMORY.md\n2. **会话路由** —— OpenClaw 需要对应配置 agent→workspace 的映射（现在 agent 配置里 workspace 字段指向哪里？）\n3. **migration** —— 现有的 workspace-main / workspace-selector 要合并还是保留？\n\n你打算怎么推这个？如果要落地，我来帮你理配置和迁移步骤。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8462,"output":797,"cacheRead":22528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778223383676,"responseId":"064cbc18520a39a81b2f5ecbe8ce5805"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0faa69bf","parentId":"477dbdd9","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:03:59.779Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b50ece374d8a8c22c38ed2307a65]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: [Replying to: \"你觉得这个结构怎么样和现在相比\n~/.openclaw/\n├── openclaw.json           # 全局路由和通道配置\n├── skills/                 # 全局技能库（放 nano-banana-pro, seedance2.0 等）\n├── workspace-lead/         # 大总管工作区 (含 SOUL.md, AGENTS.md)\n├── workspace-geo/          # GEO内容优化师工作区\n├── workspace-reddit/       # Reddit营销专家工作区\n└── workspace-tiktok/       # TikTok爆款编导工作区\"]\n\n1，按照这个目录结构来看的话， skills 就是共享的。 如果是只有当前agent可用。 是不是 在自己workspace下面还要单独色设置吗？\n2，不懂，\n3，是和我提出的结构一样吗\nReply target of current user message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"你觉得这个结构怎么样和现在相比\\n~/.openclaw/\\n├── openclaw.json           # 全局路由和通道配置\\n├── skills/                 # 全局技能库（放 nano-banana-pro, seedance2.0 等）\\n├── workspace-lead/         # 大总管工作区 (含 SOUL.md, AGENTS.md)\\n├── workspace-geo/          # GEO内容优化师工作区\\n├── workspace-reddit/       # Reddit营销专家工作区\\n└── workspace-tiktok/       # TikTok爆款编导工作区\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1778223839695}}
