{"type":"message","id":"c2b3c3ad","parentId":"bf544e18","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:04:41.292Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User has 3 questions. Let me address each:\n\n1. If skills are shared globally, does each workspace need its own skills folder? If an agent only needs a specific skill, should it be placed in its own workspace?\n\n2. They don't understand what I meant by \"session routing\" - what I meant was how OpenClaw maps which agent uses which workspace. This is configured in openclaw.json. Let me try to explain.\n\n3. Are they asking if the current structure is the same as what they proposed? No - current structure is `workspace/` with date-indexed directories, NOT the workspace-lead/geo/reddit/tiktok structure they proposed.\n\n\nI realize I couldn't access the config due to a gateway identity error, so I should work with what I can observe from the directory structure. Looking at the actual filesystem, I can see the skills are scattered between `workspace/skills` and `plugin-skills/`, while the workspace itself contains those date-indexed directories rather than agent-specific folders. This tells me the current setup doesn't match their proposed structure at all.\n","thinkingSignature":"122f7c55bddad520261cb39684f2030b45e58e006adccfc0f5a2561009bb0c0d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n1. **Skills 放哪取决于作用域**：\n   - 全局通用技能（如 searxng-search、weather）→ 放 `~/.openclaw/skills/`，所有 Agent 都能用\n   - 某个 Agent 专属的技能 → 放在它自己的 workspace 里，如 `workspace-geo/.skills/`\n   - **不需要每个 workspace 都放一份**——OpenClaw 启动 Agent 时会从它的 workspace + 全局 skills 两处加载\n\n2. **\"会话路由\"是什么意思**：\n   意思是：OpenClaw 怎么知道\"大总管\"这个 Agent 用哪个 workspace？\n   \n   这在 `openclaw.json` 里配置，叫 `workspace` 字段。每个 agent 可以指定不同的 `workspace` 路径。这样当你说\"把任务发给 GEO 内容优化师\"，它就会去 `workspace-geo/` 读自己的 SOUL.md/MEMORY.md，**不会和大总管的上下文混在一起**。\n\n3. **当前结构和你提的不一样**：\n   \n   当前（混乱）：\n   ```\n   workspace/\n   ├── 2026-04-10/\n   ├── 2026-04-12/\n   ├── ...（45个按日期分的目录）\n   ├── workspace-main/    ← 大总管主会话\n   ├── workspace-selector/  ← 选品Agent\n   └── skills/           ← skills散落在这\n   ```\n   \n   你提的（清晰）：\n   ```\n   workspace-lead/      ← 大总管\n   workspace-geo/       ← GEO优化师\n   workspace-reddit/     ← Reddit营销\n   workspace-tiktok/     ← TikTok编导\n   ```\n   \n   核心区别：按**角色/职责**命名，而不是按日期堆。\n\n要落地的话，我现在可以帮你把 `openclaw.json` 里各 agent 的 workspace 路径理清楚，迁移文件。推进吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30288,"output":605,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32429,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778223839791,"responseId":"064cbde052d6d0f66f5d16bcfcc48930"}}
