{"type":"message","id":"21c8c98d","parentId":"30bddf00","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:08:18.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the current structure. Let me analyze:\n\nCurrent agents:\n1. `main` - no workspace specified (uses default), identity: KITT-AGI\n2. `tts` - workspace: `e-commerce/sourcing` (relative to workspace root)\n\nCurrent structure:\n- `workspace/` has 45 date-indexed directories (clutter)\n- There's `workspace-main/` and `workspace-selector/` at the same level\n- Skills are in `workspace/skills/`\n- The `tts` agent's workspace points to `e-commerce/sourcing` (a subdirectory of `workspace/`)\n\nThe proposed structure:\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── openclaw.json           # Global routing and channel config\n├── skills/                 # Global skills (shared)\n\n\n├── workspace-lead/         # Lead Agent workspace (SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, etc.)\n├── workspace-geo/          # GEO Content Optimizer workspace\n├── workspace-reddit/       # Reddit Marketing Expert workspace\n└── workspace-tiktok/       # TikTok Viral Script Writer workspace\n```\n\nThe current agent list only has `main` and `tts`, but the user is now describing four distinct roles: the Lead Agent, GEO Content Optimizer, Reddit Marketing Expert, and TikTok Viral Script Writer. This suggests either new agents are being planned or the existing `tts` agent needs to be split into multiple specialized agents.\n\nTo implement this proposed structure, I need to create separate workspace directories for each role, update the openclaw.json configuration to reference these new workspaces, and establish the appropriate bindings between accounts and agents—particularly noting that the `kiit` account currently handles the main agent routing.\n","thinkingSignature":"a17661fc6df8f48d4d57d98af80427b26857b77a47e739c76f62c665c560abd1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，现状全部理清了。给你对比：\n\n---\n\n## 📊 现状盘点\n\n**Agents（现在只有2个）：**\n| Agent ID | 名称 | Workspace | 绑定的飞书账号 |\n|----------|------|-----------|---------------|\n| `main` | KITT-AGI | 未指定（默认） | `kiit`（大总管） |\n| `tts` | TK 选品大师 | `e-commerce/sourcing` | `tts` |\n\n**Workspace 实际结构（混乱）：**\n```\nworkspace/\n├── 2026-04-10 ~ 2026-05-04  （45个按日期堆的目录，杂）\n├── workspace-main/          ← main的历史会话\n├── workspace-selector/       ← 旧的选品会话\n├── e-commerce/\n│   ├── operations/\n│   ├── sourcing/            ← tts agent 当前workspace\n│   └── supply-chain/\n├── skills/                  ← 散落的skills\n└── social-media/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 你提出的目标结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── openclaw.json\n├── skills/                   # 全局共享skills\n├── workspace-lead/          # 大总管（承接 main）\n├── workspace-geo/           # 新增\n├── workspace-reddit/        # 新增\n└── workspace-tiktok/        # 新增\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 需要做的事\n\n| # | 动作 | 说明 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | 创建4个 workspace 目录 | `workspace-lead`, `workspace-geo`, `workspace-reddit`, `workspace-tiktok` |\n| 2 | 把 `main` agent 的 workspace 从默认改为 `workspace-lead/` | 大总管的上下文独立出来 |\n| 3 | 把 `tts` agent 的 workspace 从 `e-commerce/sourcing` 改为 `workspace-lead/tts` | 选品大师留在大总管体系内 |\n| 4 | 新增 `geo`、`reddit`、`tiktok` 三个 agent 配置 | 加到 `agents.list` 和 `bindings` |\n| 5 | 迁移文件 | `workspace-main/` → `workspace-lead/`，旧日期目录归档 |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 关键问题先确认\n\n1. **`kiit` 和 `tts` 是两个独立的飞书机器人**，对吗？也就是说 Reddit 专家、TikTok 编导也是绑定独立的飞书 bot？\n2. **`tts`（选品大师）保留在 `workspace-lead/` 下**，还是独立出去？——看你之前的描述\"选品问题 → 分配给 tts\"，所以它应该是大总管下级\n3. **现有 `workspace-main/` 里的历史会话**要保留还是归档？\n\n确认完我就出具体操作步骤。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":752,"output":917,"cacheRead":34048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778224049852,"responseId":"064cbeb21c26bfa0331ade41c6b47331"}}
