{"type":"message","id":"db0daa37","parentId":"8e783b51","timestamp":"2026-05-08T07:19:03.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying:\n1. `workspace-lead/` - don't need to rename, keep `workspace-main` as the main agent's workspace\n2. \"取消原来的分组不用了\" - cancel the original grouping (the e-commerce/sourcing/subfolders structure)\n\nSo the target is simpler:\n- `workspace-main/` stays as-is (rename from workspace-lead back to workspace-main)\n- `workspace-tts/` is new for the tts agent\n- The old `e-commerce/operations`, `e-commerce/sourcing`, `e-commerce/supply-chain` structure is being retired - no more grouping, just flat workspace directories per agent\n\nLet me confirm the simplified plan:\n\n**Final structure:**\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── skills/                   # 全局共享\n├── workspace-main/           # 大总管（main agent）- 保持现状路径\n└── workspace-tts/           # 选品大师（tts agent）- 新建\n```\n\nAnd the old `e-commerce/` directory structure gets retired/archived.\n\nLet me confirm this understanding with the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"3bfb1c9aea690f253d2039b9a94f576c114131984ad0437390ece74513181201"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，明白了。简化：\n\n**最终结构：**\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── skills/                   # 全局共享\n├── workspace-main/           # 大总管（main）—— 保持现状\n└── workspace-tts/           # 选品大师（tts）—— 新建\n```\n\n**取消的：**\n- `e-commerce/operations`、`e-commerce/sourcing`、`e-commerce/supply-chain` 这套分组结构 → 废除，tts 独立成 flat 的 `workspace-tts/`\n\n---\n\n**迁移步骤（确认版）：**\n\n| # | 动作 | 操作 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | 创建 `workspace-tts/` | mkdir |\n| 2 | 把 `tts` agent workspace 改为 `workspace-tts/` | 改 openclaw.json |\n| 3 | 把 `e-commerce/sourcing/` 内容迁移进 `workspace-tts/` | 复制/移动文件 |\n| 4 | `workspace-main/` 保持不动 | — |\n| 5 | 归档 `e-commerce/`（可选，保留历史） | mv |\n\n确认的话我就开始操作。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":698,"output":451,"cacheRead":35072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36221,